articles.author: Estacio Valoi, Tim Lister and Isa Soares, CNN
articles.title: Dozens unaccounted for in Mozambique after Islamist attack, rights groups say - CNN
articles.description: Thousands of people have fled the town of Palma in northern Mozambique after an attack by Islamist insurgents on Wednesday, according to human rights groups, while the fate of dozens of people who had taken refuge in a local hotel remains unclear.
